Nairobi &mdash; Popular musician Charles Kanyi alias Jaguar has been charged with careless driving leading to the deaths of two people on the Makutano-Sagana Road.Jaguar was arraigned before a Magistrate's Court in Kirinyaga where he denied two counts of reckless driving and was released on a Sh50,000 bond.The accident occurred two weeks ago involving Jaguar's Range Rover which hit a motor cyclist, killing him on the spot alongside his pillion passenger.